IMH Financial






 

Top



 





 





Ahead of the Future 

With over a decade of experience in real estate lending and investment, IMH Financial Corporation is ahead of the curve 







Always Seeking Opportunity 

Strategic partnerships, attractive investments and seizing the best opportunities in real estate is what makes our company tick 







Smart Growth 

We identify and purchase quality assets, investments and opportunities that facilitate strategic growth 



 




 






 



Assets Available for Sale



Search Listings













IMH Financial Corporation is a real estate investment and finance company based in the Southwest United States with over a decade of experience in various and diverse facets of the real estate lending and investment process. Our expertise spans origination, acquisition, underwriting, documentation, servicing, construction, enforcement, development, management and operations, marketing, and disposition.








 



Over ten years ago, IMH Secured Loan Fund began with a short-term bridge loan to help finance a small real estate project. It was a relationship built on trust and mutual respect — qualities that to this day, cement every long-term relationship.
Learn More





 



We understand and evaluate our borrower’s needs, then make them our own. We present options that make sense. We offer flexible loans, competitively-priced, and combined with professional service that earns trust and business for years to come.
Learn More





 



We respect our brokers as key business partners and strive to keep them informed and up to date regarding the progress of their loans. We provide our brokers with competitive compensation.
Learn More





IMH strives to maintain transparency and trust with its investors. Our commitment to our shareholders drives IMH to be the best in its class and build a strong reputation for honesty and integrity. These are among our most valuable assets.
 
The Shareholder Portal allows our investors to create a personal account granting access to the latest in shareholder news and enabling them to manage the details of their account.





