IMH Financial Corporation is a real estate investment and finance company based in the Southwest United States with over a decade of experience in various and diverse facets of the real estate lending and investment process. Our expertise spans origination, acquisition, underwriting, documentation, servicing, construction, enforcement, development, management and operations, marketing, and disposition.








 



Over ten years ago, IMH Secured Loan Fund began with a short-term bridge loan to help finance a small real estate project. It was a relationship built on trust and mutual respect — qualities that to this day, cement every long-term relationship.
Learn More





 



