Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Asset Management
Sub-Industry: Investment Companies
IMH Financial Corporation is a real estate finance company based in Scottsdale, Arizona.  The Company is involved with the acquisition and origination of min-perm loans, or other short-term financings that are used to pay off construction or commercial property loans.




